data.description: Enjoy the spaciousness and brightness of this 3 bed, 2 bath home with a den, situated on a large corner lot in the beautiful and sought-after San Lucas neighborhood. This home boasts high ceilings and plenty of natural light throughout. The kitchen, with it's massive island & elegant 42'' upper cabinets provide ample storage and counter space, and opens to a cozy living area. The formal living room and dining area are perfect for entertaining guests. Low-maintenance landscaping and solar make this home extremely utility-efficient, and the primary bathroom features a garden tub & dual vanity. This home features stunning mountain views, & easy access to Phoenix and the city via I-10. **Range Priced from $325k-$345k with generous incentives for closing costs or FREE solar for 8 years
